origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'RealEstateTechAPI.get_tech_assessment', 'description': 'This function retrieves a technology application assessment report for a specified real estate project.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'projectName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the real estate project.'}, {'name': 'reportType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of report to retrieve, e.g., application, development, impact.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'The technology application assessment report for the project.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 RealEstateTechAPI.get_tech_assessment, 它的参数输入如下: 'projectName'是'GreenTech Estates', 'reportType'是'application'.
